N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 1105.5 - Examination results: reporting

State Regulations

An approved examination administrator shall report
examination results to each examinee and the Department of State in such form
and in such manner as shall be prescribed by the department. Notes
